snippet.title: PAKO - Car Chase Simulator iOS launch trailer
snippet.description:
Closed area. No Escape. How long would you last?

PAKO is now available for iOS and Windows Phone. 
(Android: October 23)

Get it here: https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/id903183877

facebook.com/PAKOTMG
twitter.com/treemengames

Free version: http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/pako/c35daa9b-e996-4a70-8515-1b36442cd9ea
